^BShell Tips^b

    Test if array ^NMYARRAY^n exists safely with ^Nnounset^n
        ^B((^$^{^b^NMYARRAY^n^S[*]^s^B+^b^N1^n^}^B))^b

    The following characters are ^BNOT^b legal in function names:

        ^" quotation mark       ^' apostrophe       ^` grave accent
        ^( left parenthesis     ^| bar              ^) right parenthesis
        ^# number sign          ^$ dollar sign      ^; semicolon
        ^< less than            ^S=^s equal            ^> greater than
        ^& ampersand            ^* asterisk         ^? question mark
        ^[ bracket left         ^\ backslash

